item.title: About fish.farmR
item.description: This is an ‘open notebook’ that is focused on the application of R-based tools to gather and explore data sets relevant to aquaculture operations, finance, and economics. I identify with my ignorance and not with my knowledge on the topic. So come along with me as I bumble through! Robert P. McGuinn 2019-12-21 Charleston, South Carolina, USA
